Variable index 
--------------
phi - signed distance function 
psi - heaviside function 
nIB - number of interface point markers 
imax, jmax - total numer of points in x and y directions 
eps_i - order of thickness of initial interface 
eps - order of grid resolution 
xg, yg - coordinates of grid points 
x, y - coordinates of cell centres 
ncap - normals to the two-phase interface 
psi_f - Heaviside function at the cell faces 
n_f - interface normals at cell faces 
psi_xx, psi_yy - second derivatives of the heaviside function 
